com.wookler.server.common

Class TimeWindow

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wookler.server.common.TimeWindow

  • public class TimeWindow
extends Object
    Class represent a time window definition. Definition includes a Granularity (MILLI, SEC., MIN, etc.) and resolution (multiplier for this granularity).
    Author:
    Subho Ghosh (subho dot ghosh at outlook.com)

      • parse

        public static TimeWindow parse(String unit)
                        throws TimeWindowException
        Parse the passed string as Time window. Time Window formats: [VALUE][UNIT] UNITS: - ms : milliseconds - ss : seconds - mm : minutes - hh : hours - dd : days
